{"tid":656173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到坐程車都會變成坐上咗個男人度...","createTime":"2018-05-07T04:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T10:45:42.000Z","uid":125434,"like":1870,"dislike":157,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"61491bfcac52d87e89208cb5ada42a8f6ffa75e4","tid":656173,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"最近天氣比較熱，可能因為着得少布咗嘅關係，一上地鐵就覺得俾啲男人眼甘甘咁望住...過咗兩個站之後就有個男人坐咗我隔離，佢都幾結實，應該有做開運動，一坐埋嚟就好大陣男人味...唔臭的，但係都唔係香。咁我就刻意坐開少少，點知佢開始慢慢貼埋嚟，用佢隻毛腳hi我對腳，可能因為我男朋友無乜腳毛...老實講我覺得個質感幾刺激...於是我下面就開始慢慢有反應...佢見我怕怕醜醜，開始有所行動...<br />\n<br />\n佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我好似邊度見過你咁，你係咪讀緊U㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我...我讀恆管㗎...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁啱嘅，我依加條水管都好痕<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢佢呢句真係挑逗...搞到我都忍唔住啦...好想要...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：依，乜你份人咁幽默嘅？咁你又係讀恆管㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔係呀，我城大㗎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁啱嘅，我性慾都好大㗎...<br />\n<br />\n就係咁我就上咗佢宿舍...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如浸大先啦？<br />\n<br />\n我最初聽唔明，以為佢約咗個浸大嘅同學一齊玩3P，原來佢係話一齊沖涼，浸大條巨龍先...<br />\n<br />\n見佢咁鍾意玩，佢一除褲我就話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：理大...你好大...<br />\n<br />\n我一除褲，佢回應翻我：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嶺..嶺大！！你條撚都好大！！！<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，我地就大戰咗幾回合，玩到中大...中門大開埋先走，估唔到坐程車都會變成坐上咗個男人度。"},{"pid":"1d51d92e97b807cd1be1c415f22053a1660a072c","tid":656173,"uid":76945,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"c22e3b08485b419d604fd67198b277902efcd841","tid":656173,"uid":3037,"like":139,"dislike":5,"score":134,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">This</span></span>"},{"pid":"15df02332cd5131b39f9f74d36d83e8209d2d6ab","tid":656173,"uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":157,"score":-153,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"見佢咁鍾意玩，佢<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一除褲</span></strong>我就話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">理大...你好大...</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18534b9bafcf50877d2690578119b14c00dfc5e2","tid":656173,"uid":44902,"like":325,"dislike":5,"score":320,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"i大 嗌到大哂"},{"pid":"c1dd16b36eb04834088d1234440fbdfd51491ae3","tid":656173,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe3db0ab0b72bcda56324dce4342c99ac848b19","tid":656173,"uid":23707,"like":23,"dislike":7,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"0a5c3c87e795cdc0b8653b2d02ba651cfad3ac75","tid":656173,"uid":3189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9c64e6eea2723fb0588cc6457eeb27ff1bfcdc","tid":656173,"uid":182688,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"中大...中門大開"},{"pid":"fddcf2970a20446a0bc2cdfefb9af5bbe964f65a","tid":656173,"uid":13653,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"有無下集 加埋